Hey, little boy.
Wie alt bist du, huh?

710
00:57:24,000 --> 00:57:27,719
Na, wie hiesst du?
Wie heisst du, huh?

711
00:57:27,800 --> 00:57:30,280
Keine Koffer,
hab'ich gesagt!

712
00:57:30,360 --> 00:57:32,719
Packt keine Koffer!
Keine Koffer!

713
00:57:32,800 --> 00:57:35,840
'Rueber zum Platz Chodi!
Koffer hierlassen!

714
00:57:35,920 --> 00:57:38,760
Blauschein.
Platz Chodi!

715
00:57:38,840 --> 00:57:41,000
Was soll
der Koffer hier?

716
00:57:41,079 --> 00:57:44,079
Alles 'rueber
zum Platz Chodi!

717
00:57:59,159 --> 00:58:00,880
We're getting out
through the sewers.

718
00:58:00,920 --> 00:58:03,559
I have to check
if they're clear.

719
00:58:03,639 --> 00:58:06,599
Mila, pack some things. Nothing bigger
than this. I can't go in the sewers.

720
00:58:06,679 --> 00:58:09,760
I told you I won't go
in the sewers.

721
00:58:12,639 --> 00:58:16,000
You can go.
Yes, you can.

722
00:58:18,039 --> 00:58:20,000
I won't go in the sewers.

723
00:58:30,400 --> 00:58:34,679
Move! Over there!
Over there! Move!

724
00:58:34,719 --> 00:58:36,920
Your card, Jew!

725
00:58:36,960 --> 00:58:39,320
Deine Papiere,
Jude!

726
00:58:39,360 --> 00:58:41,960
Deine Papiere, Jude!

727
00:58:43,320 --> 00:58:45,840
That line.

728
00:58:45,920 --> 00:58:47,159
Deine Karte!

729
00:58:47,199 --> 00:58:50,840
Ich geh'nicht 'rauf
wegen Deiner verdammten Karte!

730
00:58:51,880 --> 00:58:54,400
Deine Scheisskarte!

731
00:59:12,280 --> 00:59:14,559
Was soll denn die Scheisse?
Bist du denn verrueckt geworden?

732
00:59:14,599 --> 00:59:17,000
Mit diesem Scheissgewehr haettest
du mich erschiessen koennen!

733
00:59:17,079 --> 00:59:19,079
Du hast so nah an mir
vorbeigeschossen!

734
00:59:19,159 --> 00:59:21,519
Was heisst hier Entschuldigung.
Du bist wohl verrueckt geworden!

735
00:59:21,559 --> 00:59:24,639
Zurueckbleiben!
Zurueckbleiben!

736
00:59:28,800 --> 00:59:32,440
Nicht sprechen, nicht sprechen!
Einfach zu den Lastwagen gehen!

737
00:59:32,519 --> 00:59:35,000
Weiterlaufen! Weiterlaufen!
Nicht sprechen!

738
00:59:44,800 --> 00:59:46,559
Komm her, du Judensau!

739
00:59:46,639 --> 00:59:48,800
Bleib stehen, hab'ich gesagt.
Bleib stehen!

740
00:59:59,800 --> 01:00:02,760
Chodzcie tu szybko!

741
01:00:44,119 --> 01:00:46,519
She's good as dead.
Leave her.

742
01:00:46,599 --> 01:00:50,039
Give me a moment.
Just let me bring her inside.

743
01:00:55,320 --> 01:00:58,880
You can join her...
or join the line.

744
01:01:03,519 --> 01:01:05,719
Women to the left! Wilhelm! Rose!

745
01:01:05,800 --> 01:01:08,559
Men to right.
Women to the left.

746
01:01:08,639 --> 01:01:11,239
Women to the left. Let me
go! I won't leave my husband!

747
01:01:15,880 --> 01:01:19,320
Women to the left, and men to
the right. Promise me, be safe.

748
01:01:21,159 --> 01:01:24,159
Your government
is in the wrong country!

749
01:01:29,800 --> 01:01:31,960
Mama! Mama!

750
01:02:18,239 --> 01:02:20,039
Mila!

751
01:02:44,960 --> 01:02:48,440
Oh, God, Danka!

752
01:02:52,239 --> 01:02:54,880
You have a Blauschein.
Blauschein doesn't matter anymore.

753
01:02:54,920 --> 01:02:57,559
They are cleaning out the ghetto.
There's not enough room for you.

754
01:02:57,639 --> 01:03:01,159
What are you talking about? We tried it
before. There's more than enough room.

755
01:03:01,199 --> 01:03:04,159
- I changed my mind!
- Mama!


